{"data":[{"date":"10:15 24/07","title":"HLV Milan n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi Bonucci c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 sang M.U ho\u1eb7c Real?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2017/6/28/hlv-gattuso-muon-bonucci-o-lai-milan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Gattuso mu\u1ed1n Bonucci \u1edf l\u1ea1i Milan. Hi\u1ec7n trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea3 Man United v\u00e0 Real Madrid.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Bonucci \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c M.U v\u00e0 Real \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Leonardo Bonucci chuy\u1ec3n t\u1eeb Juventus sang AC Milan v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 42 tri\u1ec7u Euro. Anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 Trung Qu\u1ed1c c\u1ee7a Rossoneri th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi mong mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i h\u00e0o quang x\u01b0a.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u1eadp t\u1ee9c, Bonucci \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao chi\u1ebfc b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Milan. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 31 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch nghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Gattuso mu\u1ed1n Bonucci \u1edf l\u1ea1i Milan d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real v\u00e0 MU \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Gattuso mu\u1ed1n Bonucci \u1edf l\u1ea1i Milan d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Real v\u00e0 MU \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/6/28/hlv-gattuso-muon-bonucci-o-lai-milan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Real l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ea1i gia quan t\u00e2m Bonucci</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 sau 1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin Bonucci c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Milan \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n. Nh\u1eefng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 Man United, Real Madrid hay Paris Saint-Germain \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7t tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Italia v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Gattuso hy v\u1ecdng h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u1edf l\u1ea1i</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Milan \u0111ang \u1edf M\u1ef9 tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu International Champions Cup. Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean, HLV Gattuso mu\u1ed1n Bonucci \u1edf l\u1ea1i Milan. \u201cT\u01b0\u01a1ng lai? T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft\u201d, \u00f4ng n\u00f3i. \u201cMi\u1ec5n l\u00e0 Bonucci c\u00f2n thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Milan, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"trung ve Bonucci Milan\" title=\"trung ve Bonucci Milan\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/17/mu-nhan-don-dau-vu-bonucci.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV Gattuso mu\u1ed1n Bonucci \u1edf l\u1ea1i Milan</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 tinh th\u1ea7n chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh trong \u0111\u1ed9i. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng Bonucci c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb tinh th\u1ea7n to l\u1edbn. Khi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh ra \u0111i, HLV v\u00e0 c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean trong \u0111\u1ed9i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf l\u1ea1i. V\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t kinh t\u1ebf, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc. M\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a m\u1edbi, Milan \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi bao g\u1ed3m th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Pepe Reina, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh Ivan Strinic v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Alen Halilovic.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Serie A tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/bayern-bao-gia-mua-vidal-cho-2-dai-gia-thanh-milan-176-191832.html\">Bayern b\u00e1o gi\u00e1 mua Vidal cho 2 \u0111\u1ea1i gia th\u00e0nh Milan</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-nhan-don-dau-vu-bonucci-172-191595.html\">MU nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00f2n \u0111au v\u1ee5 sao kh\u1ee7ng Italia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-no-luc-chieu-mo-sat-thu-serie-a-180-191701.html\">Real mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u201cs\u00e1t th\u1ee7\u201d Serie A \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-italia/da-xong-tuong-lai-cua-tien-dao-mauro-icardi-176-191546.html\">\u0110\u00e3 xong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mauro Icardi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-lam-dieu-nay-de-chieu-mo-bang-duoc-ivan-perisic-172-191494.html\">MU l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ivan Perisic</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4556","checkdouble":"191897"},{"date":"09:14 24/07","title":"Gi\u00e1 v\u00e9 xem U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 \u1ebf v\u00ec qu\u00e1 cao","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/gia-ve-xem-u23-viet-nam-thi-dau-co-nguy-co-e-vi-qua-cao.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e1 v\u00e9 xem U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 8 t\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1n v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng BTC gi\u1ea3i b\u1ecb \"\u1ebf v\u00e9\" l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao.\r\n</h2><h2>Gi\u00e1 v\u00e9 xem U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u00e1 cao</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho \u0111\u1ea1i h\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 thao ch\u00e2u \u00c1 ASIAD 2018, L\u0110B\u0110 Vi\u1ec7t Nam VFF \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 Vinaphone t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf n\u0103m 2018.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1ea3i s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 3/8 \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y 7/8/2018, t\u1ea1i SV\u0110QG M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh (H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i), quy t\u1ee5 4 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, U23 Uzbekistan, U23 Oman v\u00e0 U23 Palestine.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\" Gi\u00e1 v\u00e9 xem U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 \u1ebf v\u00ec qu\u00e1 cao h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\" Gi\u00e1 v\u00e9 xem U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 \u1ebf v\u00ec qu\u00e1 cao h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/gia-ve-xem-u23-viet-nam-thi-dau-co-nguy-co-e-vi-qua-cao.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Gi\u00e1 v\u00e9 xem U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 \u1ebf v\u00ec qu\u00e1 cao</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i sau th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1/2018, l\u00fac n\u00e0y th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn, NHM. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u00fd do Vinaphone \u0111\u1ee9ng ra t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 cho gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1eed l\u1eeda quan tr\u1ecdng n\u00e0y tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham gia Gi\u1ea3i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf U23 - C\u00fap Vinaphone 2018 c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n s\u1ebd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00e3 tham d\u1ef1 VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018, t\u1ea1i Th\u01b0\u1eddng Ch\u00e2u - Trung Qu\u1ed1c h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 1/2018. Tr\u00ean c\u01a1 s\u1edf quy \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ee7a ASIAD 18 l\u00e0 U23 + 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i n\u00ean c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ban t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3i \u0111ang \u0111\u1eb7t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1 ra m\u1ed9t m\u1ee9c v\u00e9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao cho m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, gi\u00e1 v\u00e9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 c\u00f3 4 m\u1ec7nh gi\u00e1: 150.000 \u0111\u1ed3ng, 200.000 \u0111\u1ed3ng, 300.000 \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 400.000 \u0111\u1ed3ng. \u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 \"m\u1ec1m\" n\u1ebfu so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn B\u00e1n k\u1ebft l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi Indonesia t\u1ea1i AFF Cup 2016, di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng qu\u1ed1c gia M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u00e1 v\u00e9 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 g\u1ed3m 4 m\u1ec7nh gi\u00e1: 150.000 \u0111\u1ed3ng, 250.000 \u0111\u1ed3ng, 300.000 \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 400.000 \u0111\u1ed3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0o t\u1edbi b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. V\u00ec th\u1ebf r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u00e1nh ngang v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn. Ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3, gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu n\u00ean kh\u00f3 \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c, ngay c\u1ea3 v\u1edbi U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng C\u0110V U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp xem nh\u1eefng C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng, Quang H\u1ea3i.. thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i hi\u1ebfm c\u00f3. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng C\u0110V \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 tr\u00ean c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng \u00edt ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ea3i c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4555","checkdouble":"191889"},{"date":"09:37 24/07","title":"\u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i U21 tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/nhat-ban-tiep-tuc-cu-doi-u21-tham-du-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>N\u1ebfu k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 x\u00e1o tr\u1ed9n, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed9i U21 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng ASIAD 2018.</h2><h2>Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i U21 tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018\u00a0</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ea1nh tranh Huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ea1i th\u1ebf v\u1eadn h\u1ed9i Olympic Tokyo 2020, b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb kh\u00e1 k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt c\u0169ng s\u1ebd c\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i U21 tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/nhat-ban-tiep-tuc-cu-doi-u21-tham-du-asiad-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd c\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i U21 tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc M\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi m\u1ecdc trui r\u00e8n kinh nghi\u1ec7m, b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n trong hai n\u0103m n\u1eefa.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i U21 tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD l\u00e0 tin vui v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo b\u1edfi theo k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m, ch\u00fang ta n\u1eb1m c\u00f9ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi m\u1ecdc.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i, hai \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p nhau. Vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 thua k\u00e9m 2 tu\u1ed5i, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc U21 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. Tuy nhi\u00ean c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 xem th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y b\u1edfi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc M\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi m\u1ecdc lu\u00f4n \u1edf m\u1ed9t tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">U21 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 x\u1ee9 Hoa anh \u0111\u00e0o v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 n\u0103m 2016. Tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chinh ph\u1ee5c ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ee7a Quang H\u1ea3i, Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1eadm 3-0.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/gia-ve-xem-u23-viet-nam-thi-dau-co-nguy-co-e-vi-qua-cao-168-191889.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/gia-ve-xem-u23-viet-nam-thi-dau-co-nguy-co-e-vi-qua-cao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/gia-ve-xem-u23-viet-nam-thi-dau-co-nguy-co-e-vi-qua-cao-168-191889.html\">Gi\u00e1 v\u00e9 xem U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 \u1ebf v\u00ec qu\u00e1 cao</span><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e1 v\u00e9 xem U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 8 t\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1n v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng BTC gi\u1ea3i b\u1ecb \u1ebf v\u00e9 l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/so-vao-bang-kho-indonesia-hoan-le-boc-tham-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-292-191883.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/so-vao-bang-kho-indonesia-hoan-le-boc-tham-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/so-vao-bang-kho-indonesia-hoan-le-boc-tham-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-292-191883.html\">S\u1ee3 v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng kh\u00f3, Indonesia ho\u00e3n l\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nIndonesia quy\u1ebft tr\u00ec ho\u00e3n vi\u1ec7c b\u1ed1c th\u0103m l\u1ea1i m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018 khi v\u1eabn c\u00f2n s\u00f3t UAE v\u00e0 Palestine v\u00ec s\u1ee3 s\u1ebd r\u01a1i v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4554","checkdouble":"191891"},{"date":"11:08 24/07","title":"\"S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n r\u1ed3i\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/sam-ngoc-duc-pham-loi-tho-bao-nhieu-lan-roi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edfng Ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt VFF, \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n H\u1ea3i H\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n n\u00ean ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c r\u0103n \u0111e v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa CLB TP.HCM vs Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t, S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o khi \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ebf H\u01b0ng. T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2 \u0111ang l\u01a1 l\u1eedng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sam Ngoc Duc pham loi tho bao voi The Hung trong tran gap Than Quang Ninh.\" title=\"S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o v\u1edbi Th\u1ebf H\u01b0ng trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/sam-ngoc-duc-pham-loi-tho-bao-nhieu-lan-roi.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o v\u1edbi Th\u1ebf H\u01b0ng trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nChia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean TTVH, \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n H\u1ea3i H\u01b0\u1eddng - Tr\u01b0\u1edfng Ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt VFF - kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n c\u00f3 h\u00e0nh vi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb9p: &quot;Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f2n nh\u1edb n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c khi c\u00f2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho \u0111\u1ed9i H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 8 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 ph\u1ea1t ti\u1ec1n 30 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi ph\u1ea3i chi tr\u1ea3 to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n chi ph\u00ed ch\u1eefa tr\u1ecb cho Anh H\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng v\u00ec h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ea1p b\u00f3ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o ch\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n&quot;.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;H\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 5 n\u0103m nay, t\u1ea1i C\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia, ch\u00ednh S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 4 tr\u1eadn sau khi v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o v\u1edbi Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9i SLNA. Khi \u1ea5y n\u1ebfu V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng r\u00fat ch\u00e2n l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 nh\u1ea3y tr\u00e1nh k\u1ecbp m\u00e0 c\u1ee9 ham b\u00f3ng th\u00ec c\u0169ng g\u00e3y \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00e2n r\u1ed3i. L\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng b\u1ea1o l\u1ef1c li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp nh\u01b0 v\u1eady theo t\u00f4i l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c&quot;.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a n\u00e0y, S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn 6 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng, 2 th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf v\u00ec nh\u1eefng pha b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb9p \u1edf V-League v\u00e0 C\u00fap Qu\u1ed1c gia. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng t\u1eebng b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 4 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 20 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng ti\u1ec1n ph\u1ea1t.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7n \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng Nguy\u1ec5n H\u1ea3i H\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c r\u0103n \u0111e v\u1edbi h\u00e0nh vi ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o c\u00f3 h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c. \u00d4ng c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1ec1 v\u1ee5 vi\u1ec7c khi c\u1ea7n h\u1ecdp Ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ra \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t khi V-League 2018 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 6 v\u00f2ng n\u1eefa s\u1ebd k\u1ebft th\u00fac.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau v\u1ee5 vi\u1ec7c, Ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o CLB TP.HCM c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi xin l\u1ed7i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Th\u1ebf H\u01b0ng, CLB Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9. Theo \u00f4ng H\u01b0\u1eddng, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m nh\u01b0ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng v\u00ec th\u1ebf m\u00e0 gi\u1ea3m nh\u1eb9 \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nan-nhan-cua-sam-ngoc-duc-mong-muon-dieu-nay-sau-cu-dap-troi-giang-168-191901.html\">N\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y sau c\u00fa \u0111\u1ea1p tr\u1eddi gi\u00e1ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chu-tich-huu-thang-noi-gi-khi-sam-ngoc-duc-pham-loi-tho-bao-168-191885.html\">Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch H\u1eefu Th\u1eafng n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-miura-noi-gi-khi-chung-kien-hoc-tro-da-tho-bao-168-191820.html\">HLV Miura n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i v\u00ec thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/vleague/clb-tphcm-keu-troi-vi-luc-luong-sam-ngoc-duc-duoc-giam-an-treo-gio-291-187003.html\">CLB TP.HCM k\u00eau tr\u1eddi v\u00ec l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3m \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/vleague/sau-khi-cong-vinh-tu-chuc-thay-tro-hlv-miura-nhan-them-tin-du-291-185533.html\">Sau khi C\u00f4ng Vinh t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Miura nh\u1eadn th\u00eam tin d\u1eef</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/vleague/bi-to-choi-tho-bao-dinh-luat-va-sam-ngoc-duc-co-nguy-co-bi-phat-291-185455.html\">B\u1ecb t\u1ed1 ch\u01a1i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o, \u0110\u00ecnh Lu\u1eadt v\u00e0 S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t b\u1ed5 sung</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4553","checkdouble":"191892"},{"date":"10:03 24/07","title":"N\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y sau c\u00fa \u0111\u1ea1p tr\u1eddi gi\u00e1ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/25/nan-nhan-cua-sam-ngoc-duc-mong-muon-dieu-nay-sau-cu-dap-troi-giang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi, \"n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n\" trong pha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n Th\u1ebf H\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 hy v\u1ecdng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p cho nhau.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"N\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y sau c\u00fa \u0111\u1ea1p tr\u1eddi gi\u00e1n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"N\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y sau c\u00fa \u0111\u1ea1p tr\u1eddi gi\u00e1n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/Nan-nhan-cua-Sam-Ngoc-Duc-mong-muon-dieu-nay-sau-cu-dap-troi-gian-hinh-anh.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7\u00a0Th\u1ebf H\u01b0ng n\u1eb1m s\u00e2n sau c\u00fa \u0111\u1ea1p tr\u1eddi gi\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a S\u1ea7m</em>\u00a0<em>Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c. \u1ea2nh: Zing.vn</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa hai CLB TP.HCM v\u00e0 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 22/7 t\u1edbi, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 pha v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Th\u1ebf H\u01b0ng b\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn. Sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y, Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, c\u00f2n Th\u1ebf H\u01b0ng c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng qu\u00e1 nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi xin l\u1ed7i t\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p b\u00ean ph\u00eda Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh. Song Th\u1ebf H\u01b0ng v\u1eabn hy v\u1ecdng Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c s\u1ebd bi\u1ebft ti\u1ebft ch\u1ebf c\u1ea3m x\u00fac \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef 'n\u1ed3i c\u01a1m' cho nhau.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh chia s\u1ebb: \"T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng qua r\u1ed3i n\u00ean t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn n\u1eefa. T\u00f4i may m\u1eafn khi kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb g\u00ec. Ch\u1ec9 mong Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c sau n\u00e0y \u0111\u1eebng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u00e1c \u00fd v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u1eefa. \u0110\u00f4i ch\u00e2n gi\u00fap c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ki\u1ebfm c\u01a1m n\u00ean \u0111\u1eebng c\u1ed1 \u00fd tri\u1ec7t h\u1ea1 l\u1eabn nhau\".</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p. Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 c\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia 2018, S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf sau pha v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u1edbi Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a CLB TP.HCM b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 3 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t 15 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3ng.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/vleague/sam-ngoc-duc-pham-loi-tho-bao-nhieu-lan-roi-291-191892.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/sam-ngoc-duc-pham-loi-tho-bao-nhieu-lan-roi.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/vleague/sam-ngoc-duc-pham-loi-tho-bao-nhieu-lan-roi-291-191892.html\">S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n r\u1ed3i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chu-tich-huu-thang-noi-gi-khi-sam-ngoc-duc-pham-loi-tho-bao-168-191885.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/28/chu-tich-huu-thang-noi-gi-khi-sam-ngoc-duc-pham-loi-tho-bao.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chu-tich-huu-thang-noi-gi-khi-sam-ngoc-duc-pham-loi-tho-bao-168-191885.html\">Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch H\u1eefu Th\u1eafng n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o?</span><br />\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u00e0 S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n qua, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch CLB TP.HCM Nguy\u1ec5n H\u1eefu Th\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4552","checkdouble":"191901"},{"date":"09:49 24/07","title":"Tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, Liverpool lo s\u1ed1t v\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/22/liverpool-don-tin-du-tu-hang-thu-matip-chan-thuong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trung v\u1ec7 Joel Matip \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i chia tay gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu ICC \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 trung t\u00e2m t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u tr\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Dortmund.</h2><h2>Matip g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trung v\u1ec7 Joel Matip \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb thay ra kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n ngay trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/video/video-tong-hop-liverpool-13-dortmund-icc-2018-329-191807.html\" target=\"_blank\">tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Liverpool v\u00e0 Dortmund</span> cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n qua. HLV Jurgen Klopp lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1ec1 b\u1eafp \u0111\u00f9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn Matip ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. Nh\u01b0ng theo k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 ch\u1ea9n \u0111o\u00e1n m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t th\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u1ebft \u0111au kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201c\u0110\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf c\u01a1 kh\u00e1c. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u01a1 b\u1eafp. Hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u1ebft r\u00e1ch nh\u1ecf\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Klopp l\u1ea1c quan v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Matip\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Matip ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, Liverpool lo s\u1ed1t v\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Matip ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, Liverpool lo s\u1ed1t v\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/22/liverpool-don-tin-du-tu-hang-thu-matip-chan-thuong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Matip ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Klopp t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 lo l\u1eafng v\u1edbi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Cameroon m\u1edbi g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Dortmund, Klopp v\u1eabn hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt t\u00edch c\u1ef1c t\u1eeb c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cJoel Matip s\u1ebd r\u1eddi tr\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Liverpool t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u01a1 m\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y m\u1edbi g\u1eb7p ph\u1ea3i \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Dortmund h\u00f4m Ch\u1ee7 nh\u1eadt.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 gi\u1eefa hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t v\u00e0 l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thay ra kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00e0y c\u0169ng n\u1eb1m \u1edf g\u1ea7n ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u00f9i m\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 n\u00f3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng khi\u1ebfn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u00e1 l\u00e2u. D\u1eabu sao, Matip c\u0169ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cV\u00ec v\u1eady, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Merseyside v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c t\u1ea1i Melwood\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Matip, Liverpool s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 2 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p c\u00f9ng Van Dijk \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi l\u00e0 Joe Gomez v\u00e0 Ragnar Klavan. C\u1ea3 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p m\u1ed9t s\u1edbm m\u1ed9t chi\u1ec1u. V\u00e0 v\u00ec th\u1ebf, The Kop \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0m th\u1ee7 ph\u00e1 trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Liverpool:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-danh-sach-7-cau-thu-giup-liverpool-thu-ve-100-trieu-bang-172-191890.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! Danh s\u00e1ch 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00fap Liverpool thu v\u1ec1 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhm-liverpool-dung-ky-vong-qua-nhieu-vao-alisson-172-191888.html\">NHM Liverpool \u0111\u1eebng k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o Alisson</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4551","checkdouble":"191895"},{"date":"10:25 24/07","title":"Chelsea ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Willian cho Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/5/chelsea-chot-gia-ban-willian-cho-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea b\u00e1n Willian cho Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i chi \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca 3 l\u1ea7n h\u1ecfi mua Willian nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Sau khi Antoine Griezmann \u1edf l\u1ea1i Atletico Madrid, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Willian c\u1ee7a Chelsea.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea b\u00e1n Willian cho Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea b\u00e1n Willian cho Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/21/Chelsea-ban-Willian-cho-Barca-voi-gia-70-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca 3 l\u1ea7n h\u1ecfi mua Willian</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPhilippe Couttinho r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n Barca mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i, HLV Ernesto Valverde c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1988.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/tin-chuyen-nhuong/gui-de-nghi-lan-3-barca-quyet-mua-ngoi-sao-cua-chelsea-187-191704.html\" target=\"_blank\">Barca \u0111\u00e3 3 l\u1ea7n h\u1ecfi mua Willian</span>. L\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng song \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Chelsea th\u1eb3ng th\u1eebng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i, sau \u0111\u00f3 Barca n\u00e2ng l\u00ean 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Barca g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb th\u1ee9 3 tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 55 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, song Chelsea v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd. Theo Daily Mail, HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf l\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Willian v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea b\u00e1n Willian cho Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i chi \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil. S\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 Chelsea y\u00eau c\u1ea7u kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u0103m nay s\u1eafp b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 30, Barca s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i suy ngh\u0129 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea vs Crystal Palace Willian ghi ban\" title=\"Chelsea vs Crystal Palace Willian ghi ban\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/11/barca-nang-gia-hoi-mua-willian-cua-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Willian cho Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo The Sun, Chelsea ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n Willian cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i bi\u00ean gi\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cho m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 M.U kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i s\u1edf h\u1eefu Willian. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 \u1edf s\u00e2n Old Trafford.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Chelsea ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Willian cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd \u01b0u ti\u00ean gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u1edf l\u1ea1i thay v\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 anh ra \u0111i, b\u1edfi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 The Blues y\u00eau c\u1ea7u nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Barca ph\u1ea3i t\u1eeb b\u1ecf m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4550","checkdouble":"191898"},{"date":"10:24 24/07","title":"\"Liverpool v\u1eabn c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/24/liverpool-van-con-thieu-mot-tien-dao-dang-cap-the-gioi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Harry Kewell kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Liverpool c\u1ea7n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c m\u1ea1nh d\u1ea1n chi ti\u00eau \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>Liverpool chi ti\u00eau m\u1ea1nh tay</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 c\u1ea3ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 b\u1eadn r\u1ed9n khi li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n ch\u00e0o nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh h\u1ea1ng n\u1eb7ng. B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Naby Keita v\u00e0 Fabinho \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Anfield v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-liverpool-kich-no-bom-tan-alisson-172-191632.html\" target=\"_blank\">Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Alisson c\u0169ng m\u1edbi gia nh\u1eadp The Kop</span> v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n l\u00e0 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y bi\u1ebfn Alisson th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u01b0ng th\u1ebf v\u1eabn l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Liverpool Kewell khuy\u00ean The Kop mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Liverpool Kewell khuy\u00ean The Kop mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/liverpool-van-con-thieu-mot-tien-dao-dang-cap-the-gioi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Liverpool: Kewell khuy\u00ean Liverpool chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n khi nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean nh\u01b0 Mohamed Salah hay Virgil van Dijk \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 t\u1ed1t trong v\u00f2ng 12 th\u00e1ng qua. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Harry Kewell cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng Merseyside v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi ng\u00f4i v\u01b0\u01a1ng Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean t\u1edd Daily Express, Kewell cho hay: \u201c\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n cho th\u1ea5y h\u1ecd x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cV\u1edbi m\u1ed9t Man City qu\u00e1 to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n v\u00e0 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt th\u00ec m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecb lu m\u1edd. Nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng Liverpool \u0111ang \u0111i \u0111\u00fang h\u01b0\u1edbng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cB\u1ed9 ba t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i c\u0169ng ngh\u0129 h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c. Ph\u00f2ng tr\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p m\u1ed9t trong ba c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3. V\u1eady n\u00ean t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u1eefa\u201d.</em><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kewell k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o Liverpool m\u00f9a t\u1edbi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 k\u00eau g\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 c\u1ea3ng b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0ng Kewell c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn HLV Klopp \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201c\u0110\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i l\u1edbn v\u1edbi Liverpool. H\u1ecd v\u1eeba c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi nh\u01b0 Alexander-Arnold v\u00e0 Andrew Robertson.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cMane, Salah v\u00e0 Firmino \u0111\u1ec1u thi \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Henderson \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ec1u mong mu\u1ed1n. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 h\u01a1n theo tu\u1ed5i t\u00e1c\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Liverpool:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-don-tin-du-tu-hang-thu-matip-chan-thuong-172-191895.html\">Tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, Liverpool lo s\u1ed1t v\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-danh-sach-7-cau-thu-giup-liverpool-thu-ve-100-trieu-bang-172-191890.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! Danh s\u00e1ch 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00fap Liverpool thu v\u1ec1 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4549","checkdouble":"191900"},{"date":"11:40 24/07","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 khuy\u00ean Arsenal mua trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Juventus","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2016/10/27/juventus-41-sampdoria-cu-dup-bat-ngo-cua-trung-ve-chiellini.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Ray Parlour cho r\u1eb1ng Arsenal th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i gia c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 Chiellini s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi trong m\u01a1 d\u00e0nh cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.</h2><h2>Parlour khuy\u00ean Arsenal mua Chiellini</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Unai Emery \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1i Premier League. Nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u1edbi Stephan Lichtsteiner hay Sokratis Papastathopoulos \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111em l\u1ea1i kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft cho h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Arsenal. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Bernd Leno c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tr\u1ea5n gi\u1eef khung th\u00e0nh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u1eabu v\u1eady, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Ray Parlour cho r\u1eb1ng Arsenal v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u1edf h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ed1t d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Emery.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 khuy\u00ean Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Chiellini h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 khuy\u00ean Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Chiellini h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/10/27/juventus-41-sampdoria-cu-dup-bat-ngo-cua-trung-ve-chiellini.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Parlour khuy\u00ean Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Chiellini</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Sokratis l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u1ed1t. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ed5 \u0111i\u1ec3n gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 Tony Adams ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111i\u1ec1u ph\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb tuy\u1ebfn d\u01b0\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cSokratis c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m chinh chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e1ng n\u1ec3. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb m\u1edd \u0111i \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ec9 huy \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Sokratis c\u0169ng c\u00f3 quen bi\u1ebft v\u1edbi Aubameyang v\u00e0 Mkhitaryan. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Arsenal v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 th\u00eam n\u1eefa, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 sau khi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Sokratis v\u00e0 Lichtsteiner. H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ed9 ra qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u s\u01a1 h\u1edf \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cArsenal c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ee9ng m\u0169i ch\u1ecbu s\u00e0o v\u00e0 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u1ea3i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. Chiellini l\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 m\u01a1 \u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi Arsenal l\u00fac n\u00e0y\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Parlour khen ng\u1ee3i Lichtsteiner</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lichtsteiner hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc qua tu\u1ed5i 34. Nh\u01b0ng nhi\u1ec1u chuy\u00ean gia v\u1eabn \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung h\u1eefu hi\u1ec7u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cBellerin s\u1ebd h\u1ecdc h\u1ecfi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u1eeb Lichtsteiner, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 \u1edf kh\u00e2u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. Bellerin t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t hay nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra khi Lichtsteiner h\u00e9t v\u00e0o m\u1eb7t c\u1eadu \u1ea5y trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cLichtsteiner s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng sau nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf Juventus c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 kinh nghi\u1ec7m l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Th\u1ee5y S\u0129. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ea3 trong l\u1eabn ngo\u00e0i s\u00e2n c\u1ecf, \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 Arsenal c\u1ea7n b\u1ea5y l\u00e2u nay\u201d.<br>\r\n</em><br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Arsenal:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/nguoi-arsenal-ung-ho-tien-ve-mesut-ozil-chia-tay-doi-tuyen-duc-184-191865.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Arsenal \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mesut Ozil chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/soc-arsenal-lai-muon-mua-them-mot-thu-mon-nua-tu-bundesliga-172-191764.html\">S\u1ed1c: Arsenal l\u1ea1i mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u1eefa t\u1eeb Bundesliga</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4548","checkdouble":"191903"},{"date":"11:22 24/07","title":"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Sturridge \u1edf l\u1ea1i Liverpool l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/24/goc-nhin-sturridge-o-lai-liverpool-la-dieu-tot-cho-tat-ca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1eb7t c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi t\u1ea1i sao Daniel Sturridge \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1edd v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a r\u1eddi Liverpool sau su\u1ed1t 4 m\u00f9a \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn theo \u0111\u00fang ngh\u0129a \u0111en. M\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t cho vi\u1ec7c Sturridge \u1edf l\u1ea1i Liverpool kh\u00f4ng g\u00ec kh\u00e1c ngo\u00e0i t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a anh.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Chu\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y cay \u0111\u1eafng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGia nh\u1eadp Liverpool \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2013 t\u1eeb Chelsea, Daniel Sturridge l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng r\u00f5 n\u00e9t. Ngay tr\u1eadn ra m\u1eaft v\u1edbi Mansfield Town \u1edf v\u00f2ng 3 c\u00fap FA 4 ng\u00e0y sau, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o sinh n\u0103m 1989 \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho The Kop ch\u1ec9 sau 7 ph\u00fat c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t, m\u1ed9t kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u01b0a h\u1ebft, 2 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n sau \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea1i Premier League, Sturridge c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u &ldquo;n\u1ed5 s\u00fang&rdquo;. Anh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Liverpool \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ghi b\u00e0n trong c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean kho\u00e1c \u00e1o sau Ray Kennedy n\u0103m 1974. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 cho t\u1edbi h\u1ebft m\u00f9a 2012/13, &ldquo;Studger&rdquo; ghi t\u1edbi 11 b\u00e0n sau 16 tr\u1eadn tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng, tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ea3 Man United, Man City v\u00e0 Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Sturridge \u1edf l\u1ea1i Liverpool l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn Sturridge \u1edf l\u1ea1i Liverpool l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/Goc-nhin-Sturridge-o-lai-Liverpool-la-dieu-tot-cho-tat-ca-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Sturridge t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng khi m\u1edbi t\u1edbi Liverpool</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec3 Sturridge c\u00f3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Liverpool b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Luis Suarez. H\u1ecd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh kh\u1ea9u &ldquo;\u0111\u1ea1i b\u00e1c hai n\u00f2ng&rdquo;, gi\u00fap L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf su\u00fdt l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh. Cho t\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 36, Liverpool v\u1eabn c\u00f2n d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u Premier League. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Chelsea, n\u01a1i Steven Gerrard c\u00f3 c\u00fa tr\u01b0\u1ee3t ch\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eddi c\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a Crystal Palace 3-3 d\u00f9 d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 3-0 \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn Liverpool v\u00e0 Sturridge \u00f4m h\u1eadn. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1nh r\u01a1i c\u00fap b\u1ea1c Premier League theo c\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i n\u1ed5i. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eady, 1 n\u0103m r\u01b0\u1ee1i c\u1ee7a Sturridge t\u1ea1i Liverpool v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. T\u00ednh ra, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat sinh t\u1ea1i Birmingham ghi t\u1edbi 35 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho The Kop ch\u1ec9 sau 49 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng. H\u00ecnh b\u00f3ng v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a s\u00e2n Anfield v\u00e0 n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u00e3 l\u1edd m\u1edd xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sturridge chan thuong\" title=\"Sturridge chan thuong\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/Sturridge-chan-thuong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p anh ch\u1eefng l\u1ea1i</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ebfn nay \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1. Sturridge b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 bao nhi\u00eau trong th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00f3 th\u00ec l\u1ee5i t\u00e0n b\u1ea5y nhi\u00eau trong 4 n\u0103m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y. N\u1ed7i \u00e1m \u1ea3nh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111eo b\u00e1m anh m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch mi\u1ec7t m\u00e0i v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u1eadn t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 t\u1edbi nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng, Sturridge \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua 12 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n d\u01b0\u1ee1ng th\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u00e0i ng\u1eafn c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 trong 4 n\u0103m qua. N\u00e0o l\u00e0 \u0111\u00f9i, g\u00e2n khoeo, h\u00f4ng, \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i, b\u1eafp ch\u00e2n&hellip;, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn m\u0169i c\u00f4ng t\u1eebng khuynh \u0111\u1ea3o Premier League ch\u00ecm trong \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn c\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 x\u00e1c l\u1eabn t\u00e2m h\u1ed3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1eeb tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t Liverpool, gi\u1edd Sturridge trong m\u1eaft nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng kh\u00e1c g\u00ec &ldquo;h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i&rdquo;. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 Roberto Firmino b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat tr\u1ebb gi\u00e0u ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-tiet-lo-su-thuc-dau-long-tu-sturridge-172-189649.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/10/liverpool-tiet-lo-su-thuc-dau-long-tu-sturridge.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-tiet-lo-su-thuc-dau-long-tu-sturridge-172-189649.html\">Liverpool ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c \u0111au l\u00f2ng t\u1eeb Sturridge</span><br>\r\n<span>Liverpool b\u00e1n Daniel Sturridge \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o h\u1ecfi mua ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn h\u1eefu d\u1ee5ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn Sturridge kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p nhi\u1ec1u cho West Brom khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111em cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n \u1edf n\u1eeda sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18. \u0110i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Sturridge \u1edf l\u1ea1i Liverpool c\u0169ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf. Nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n trong m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y l\u1ea1i ch\u1ee9ng minh \u0111i\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, \u1edf 5 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t cho Liverpool (\u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng 1 hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ed5 l\u1ea1i), Sturridge \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh 1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sturridge choi tot tai Liverpool\" title=\"Sturridge choi tot tai Liverpool\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/Sturridge-choi-tot-tai-Liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Sturridge ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a 2018/19</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh m\u0169i \u0111inh ba Mane, Firmino v\u00e0 Salah \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01b0a tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u, Sturridge n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool. Khi \u0111\u00f3, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta m\u1edbi nh\u1eadn ra r\u1eb1ng ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb b\u1ed9 ba h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t tr\u00ean, nh\u1eefng &ldquo;ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eeba&rdquo; nh\u01b0 Ings, Origi, Markovic hay nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb nh\u01b0 Woodburn, Solanke \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1eb1ng Studger.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, C\u0110V c\u1ee7a Liverpool d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m v\u1edbi Sturridge. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ee9c t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 tr\u00ean h\u1ebft l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t t\u00e0i n\u0103ng. B\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat s\u1ebd tr\u00f2n 29 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 9 t\u1edbi v\u1eabn ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 63 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau 133 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 qua cho The Kop (trung b\u00ecnh (0.47 b\u00e0n/ tr\u1eadn).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sturridge can thiet cho Liverpool\" title=\"Sturridge can thiet cho Liverpool\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/Sturridge-can-thiet-cho-Liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Sturridge v\u1eabn h\u1eefu \u00edch cho Liverpool</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00e3y l\u01b0u \u00fd: Ngo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb Salah, nh\u1eefng Mane (0.45 b\u00e0n/ tr\u1eadn) v\u00e0 Firmino (0.35 b\u00e0n/ tr\u1eadn) \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t hi\u1ec7u su\u1ea5t l\u00e0m b\u00e0n cao nh\u01b0 Sturridge. L\u1eadt l\u1ea1i qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, Liverpool c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf c\u00f3 12 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 anh t\u1eeb Chelsea n\u0103m 2013. Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 xem \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00f3n h\u1eddi d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec1u g\u00ec s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra n\u1ebfu Sturridge kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng? Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a anh s\u1ebd t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea3 t\u1ea1i Liverpool v\u00e0 \u0110T Anh. Nh\u01b0ng ngay c\u1ea3 l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e2y, khi b\u1ecb v\u00ed nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t &ldquo;th\u01b0\u01a1ng binh&rdquo;, Sturridge v\u1eabn h\u1eefu \u00edch cho L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-bat-ngo-dam-bao-tuong-lai-cho-phe-pham-cua-liverpool-172-191866.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/klopp-bat-ngo-dam-bao-tuong-lai-cho-phe-pham-cua-liverpool.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-bat-ngo-dam-bao-tuong-lai-cho-phe-pham-cua-liverpool-172-191866.html\">Klopp b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai cho &ldquo;ph\u1ebf ph\u1ea9m&rdquo; c\u1ee7a Liverpool</span><br>\r\n<span>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o th\u1ea5t s\u1ee7ng Daniel Sturridge \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1edf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u1edf l\u1ea1i Anfield khi \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng \u1edf chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a Liverpool.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Jurgen Klopp c\u0169ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y nh\u01b0 v\u1eady v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1eadp t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c b\u00e1n \u0111\u1ee9t Sturridge trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y \u00edt nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng. Vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o t\u1eebng 26 l\u1ea7n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0110T Anh \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng Merseyside mang nhi\u1ec1u \u00fd ngh\u0129a t\u00edch c\u1ef1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi Sturridge, n\u1ebfu r\u1eddi Liverpool, anh ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng trung b\u00ecnh v\u00e0 nh\u1ecf. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n Sturridge \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng ph\u1ea3i tranh ch\u1ea5p b\u00f3ng, \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i ch\u00fat n\u00e0o v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n s\u1eed ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a anh. Ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 29, vi\u1ec7c sang M\u1ef9 hay ch\u00e2u \u00c1 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng c\u0169ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sturridge va Klopp\" title=\"Sturridge va Klopp\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/24/Sturridge-va-Klopp.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Klopp mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Anfield</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c, Liverpool c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n Sturridge \u1edf l\u1ea1i. Nh\u1eefng Mane, Firmino v\u00e0 Salah v\u1eabn chi\u1ebfm su\u1ea5t c\u1ee9ng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh The Kop, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i nghi ng\u1edd. Song Sturridge s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n d\u1ef1 ph\u00f2ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3i cho h\u1ecd m\u1ed7i khi c\u1ea7n k\u00edp. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng Sturridge v\u00e0 k\u00e9m xa b\u1ed9 ba MFS. S\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u00fac Liverpool c\u1ea7n b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd mong ch\u1edd s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn t\u1edbi t\u1eeb s\u1ed1 15 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem l\u1ea1i m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Sturridge qua tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng 2-0 c\u1ee7a Liverpool tr\u01b0\u1edbc Blackburn (Giao h\u1eefu)</strong>:\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/20/Blackburn-Rovers-vs-Liverpool.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Liverpool tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-don-tin-du-tu-hang-thu-matip-chan-thuong-172-191895.html\">Tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, Liverpool lo s\u1ed1t v\u00f3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-van-con-thieu-mot-tien-dao-dang-cap-the-gioi-172-191900.html\">Liverpool v\u1eabn c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-danh-sach-7-cau-thu-giup-liverpool-thu-ve-100-trieu-bang-172-191890.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! Danh s\u00e1ch 7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00fap Liverpool thu v\u1ec1 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhm-liverpool-dung-ky-vong-qua-nhieu-vao-alisson-172-191888.html\">NHM Liverpool \u0111\u1eebng k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o Alisson</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-nam-nay-se-la-nam-cua-chung-toi-172-191880.html\">Klopp: &ldquo;N\u0103m nay s\u1ebd l\u00e0 n\u0103m c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i&rdquo;</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4547","checkdouble":"191904"},{"date":"08:54 24/07","title":"Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch H\u1eefu Th\u1eafng n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/28/chu-tich-huu-thang-noi-gi-khi-sam-ngoc-duc-pham-loi-tho-bao.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u00e0 S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n qua, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch CLB TP.HCM Nguy\u1ec5n H\u1eefu Th\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Bongda24h \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa CLB TP.HCM vs Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng 20 V-League 2018 di\u1ec5n ra chi\u1ec1u 23/7, khi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 \u0111ang l\u00e0 2-1 nghi\u00eang v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 th\u00ec h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 pha \u0111\u1ea1p th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh \u1edf ph\u00fat 84.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh Tr\u1ea7n V\u0103n L\u1eadp \u1edf m\u1ed9t c\u1ef1 ly kh\u00f4ng xa \u0111\u00e3 quan s\u00e1t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat do d\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e3 r\u00fat th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tan Chu tich Nguyen Huu Thang khong dat muc tieu vao top 3 nhu Le Cong Vinh.\" title=\"T\u00e2n Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Nguy\u1ec5n H\u1eefu Th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau v\u00e0o top 3 nh\u01b0 L\u00ea C\u00f4ng Vinh.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/28/chu-tich-huu-thang-noi-gi-khi-sam-ngoc-duc-pham-loi-tho-bao.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Nguy\u1ec5n H\u1eefu Th\u1eafng x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1ecf ra \u00e2n h\u1eadn sau sai l\u1ea7m v\u1eeba qua</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb l\u00ean \u00e1n b\u1edfi h\u00e0nh vi v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng phi th\u1ec3 thao v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh n\u00e0y, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch CLB TP.HCM \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n H\u1eefu Th\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ee1 cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;H\u1ebft tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, v\u00e0o trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3, S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng k\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3m x\u00fac v\u00e0 b\u1eadt kh\u00f3c. T\u00f4i n\u00f3i th\u1ee9 nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc s\u00e2u s\u1eafc, ph\u1ea3i r\u00fat kinh nghi\u1ec7m. L\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p, \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u1eef b\u00ecnh t\u0129nh tr\u00ean s\u00e2n b\u00f3ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t, v\u00ec l\u00e0 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i kh\u00e1ng nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00e1c ph\u1ea3n c\u1ea3m nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, ph\u1ea3i lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1. S\u1ef1 vi\u1ec7c c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 qua r\u1ed3i, n\u1ebfu Th\u1ebf H\u01b0ng b\u1ecb \u0111au n\u1eb7ng ch\u1eafc c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c t\u1ed9i l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a ch\u00e1u s\u1ebd c\u00e0ng n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 h\u01a1n.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 xin l\u1ed7i Th\u1ebf H\u01b0ng v\u00e0 BHL T.Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh. Ch\u00e1u bi\u1ebft l\u1ed7i m\u00ecnh r\u1ea5t n\u1eb7ng v\u00e0 m\u1ecdi tr\u00ecnh b\u00e0y l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 th\u1eeba. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc, xin l\u1ed7i c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n Th\u1ebf H\u01b0ng, CLB T.Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 c\u1ed1 ph\u1ea3n c\u1ea3m n\u00e0y&rdquo;, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch CLB TP.HCM Nguy\u1ec5n H\u1eefu Th\u1eafng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n m\u00ecnh, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c c\u0169ng cho bi\u1ebft anh \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi xin l\u1ed7i t\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Th\u1ebf H\u01b0ng c\u1ee7a CLB T.Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ngh\u1ec7 An c\u0169ng cho bi\u1ebft s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn m\u1ecdi \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0a ra t\u1eeb ph\u00eda VFF nh\u01b0ng hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eeda ch\u1eefa sai l\u1ea7m sau \u0111\u00f3.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-miura-noi-gi-khi-chung-kien-hoc-tro-da-tho-bao-168-191820.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/24/hlv-miura-noi-gi-khi-chung-kien-hoc-tro-da-tho-bao.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-miura-noi-gi-khi-chung-kien-hoc-tro-da-tho-bao-168-191820.html\">HLV Miura n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i v\u00ec thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o?</span><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n v\u00ec l\u1ed7i v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o, HLV Toshiya Miura \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4546","checkdouble":"191885"},{"date":"07:27 24/07","title":"Xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng m\u00e0n \u201cc\u01b0\u1edbp d\u00e2u\u201d th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Malcolm","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/xuat-hien-dien-bien-khong-tuong-man-cuop-dau-thuong-vu-malcolm.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>30 ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 T\u1ebft, d\u00f9 c\u1ea3 AS Roma l\u1eabn Bordeaux \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t cu\u1ed9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, nh\u01b0ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y Barca nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o v\u1ee5 Malcolm v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb l\u1edbn h\u01a1n.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nV\u1ee5 l\u1eadt k\u00e8o kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Barca?<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong kho\u1ea3ng 2 ng\u00e0y g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Malcolm c\u1ee7a Bordeaux \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn s\u00e1t Roma v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng kho\u1ea3ng 35 tri\u1ec7u euro. V\u00e0 theo x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn t\u1eeb c\u1ea3 CLB n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p l\u1eabn \u0111\u1ed9i mua AS Roma, c\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ec1u vui v\u1ebb v\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t cho r\u1eb1ng Barca \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c, b\u1ea5t k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ed1t c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, nh\u00e0 b\u00e1o Fabrizio Romano cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Malcolm t\u1edbi Roma \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00eda Bordeaux \u0111\u01b0a ra th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c, nh\u01b0ng Barca \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng c\u01b0\u1edbp ng\u01b0\u1eddi.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o v\u1ee5 Malcolm \u0111\u00fang ph\u00fat ch\u00f3t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Barca nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o v\u1ee5 Malcolm \u0111\u00fang ph\u00fat ch\u00f3t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/190009-malcom.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o v\u1ee5 Malcolm khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1edbi Roma</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n&ldquo;L\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb l\u1edbn h\u01a1n \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1eedi t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Barca, v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Malcolm l\u00fac n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh bay t\u1edbi Italia n\u1eefa. Ph\u00eda AS Roma \u0111ang r\u1ea5t t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ngu\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi&hellip; Everton. Nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-liverpool-kich-no-bom-tan-alisson-172-191632.html\" target=\"_blank\">AS Roma sau khi b\u00e1n Alisson cho Liverpool</span> \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n ti\u1ec1n t\u1ea5n v\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Italia \u0111ang n\u1ebfm tr\u1ea3i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c b\u1ecb c\u01b0\u1edbp h\u00e0ng nh\u01b0 ch\u00ednh Everton.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 41 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Barca g\u1eedi t\u1edbi Bordeaux. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 tr\u01a1 tr\u1ebdn xu\u00f4i theo l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0y, cho d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o b\u00e1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi cho Roma. Malcolm, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean th\u00edch Barca h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Italia, v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu Barca nh\u1ea3y v\u00e0o v\u1ee5 Malcolm v\u00e0 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd bu\u00f4ng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau Willian &ndash; c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/tan-binh-cua-barca-tho-phao-vi-khong-con-phai-so-messi-180-191789.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/22/tan-binh-cua-barca-tho-phao-vi-khong-con-phai-so-messi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/tan-binh-cua-barca-tho-phao-vi-khong-con-phai-so-messi-180-191789.html\">T\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a Barca th\u1edf ph\u00e0o v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i s\u1ee3 Messi</span><br>\r\nTrung v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi gia nh\u1eadp Barca t\u1eeb Sevilla, Clement Lenglet chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Messi v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/4-dieu-xay-ra-sau-khi-liverpool-chieu-mo-alisson-becker-172-191685.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/20/totti-liverpool-da-dua-ra-loi-de-nghi-khong-the-tu-choi-o-vu-alisson.jpeg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/4-dieu-xay-ra-sau-khi-liverpool-chieu-mo-alisson-becker-172-191685.html\">4 \u0111i\u1ec1u x\u1ea3y ra sau khi Liverpool chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Alisson Becker</span><br>\r\nTh\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c mong ch\u1edd nh\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y qua \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng h\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 khi Liverppol chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Alisson th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4545","checkdouble":"191878"},{"date":"08:18 24/07","title":"Enrique c\u1ea7n gi\u00fap \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch EURO 2020","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/10/enrique-can-giup-dt-tay-ban-nha-vo-dich-euro-2020.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i v\u1edbi scandal l\u1edbn, B\u00f2 t\u00f3t \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh thay t\u01b0\u1edbng. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o David Villa \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 HLV Luis Enrique \u0111em l\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng cho \u0110T.</h2><h2><br>\r\nVilla mu\u1ed1n T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi World Cup 2018 di\u1ec5n ra 1 ng\u00e0y, \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c sa th\u1ea3i HLV Julen Lopetegui v\u00e0 b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Fernando Hierro thay th\u1ebf. Sau gi\u1ea3i, Hierro c\u0169ng r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng v\u00e0 nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho Luis Enrique &ndash; c\u1ef1u HLV c\u1ee7a Barca, v\u00e0 t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o c\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u La Liga khi c\u00f2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ecf qua s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, B\u00f2 t\u00f3t c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p v\u1ed1n c\u00f3 v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch EURO 2020. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat k\u1ef3 c\u1ef1u David Villa \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Enrique: &ldquo;Th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1eb7t ra cho \u00f4ng r\u1ea5t l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, b\u1edfi \u0110T \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ecdi danh hi\u1ec7u trong nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec9nh cao.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"David Villa \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 HLV Luis Enrique\" title=\"HLV Luis Enrique\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/1/23/dai-thang-eibar-hlv-enrique-van-chua-hai-long.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>David Villa \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 HLV Luis Enrique</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, v\u00ec v\u1eady th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra. Th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u00ecn nh\u1eadn v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 khi b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadn m\u1eaft ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng g\u00ec b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i s\u00e2n c\u1ecf. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n l\u00e0m \u0111\u00fang, c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt t\u1ed1t, b\u1ea1n th\u1eafng. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng, b\u1ea1n th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 v\u1eady.&rdquo;</div>\r\n<div>&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Khi \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 ngu\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c l\u1edbn, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y \u0110T Nga c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do h\u1ecd ti\u1ec5n T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 di\u1ec5n ra, b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo s\u1ebd l\u00e0 EURO 2020, v\u00ec v\u1eady \u00f4ng \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u1eafp r\u00e1p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ea1t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cao nh\u1ea5t, sau \u0111\u00f3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. D\u00f9 sao v\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n, t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng \u00f4ng \u1ea5y s\u1ebd \u0111em l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha&rdquo; &ndash; David Villa \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 HLV Luis Enrique.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/luis-enrique-tu-tin-tai-thiet-tay-ban-nha-184-191508.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/10/luis-enrique-tu-tin-tai-thiet-tay-ban-nha.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/luis-enrique-tu-tin-tai-thiet-tay-ban-nha-184-191508.html\">Luis Enrique t\u1ef1 tin t\u00e1i thi\u1ebft T\u00e2y Ban Nha</span><br>\r\nT\u00e2n HLV 48 tu\u1ed5i tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho nh\u1eefng th\u1eed th\u00e1ch tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ldbd-tay-ban-nha-nai-ni-pique-dung-chia-tay-dtqg-421-190823.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/ldbd-tay-ban-nha-nai-ni-pique-dung-chia-tay-dtqg.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ldbd-tay-ban-nha-nai-ni-pique-dung-chia-tay-dtqg-421-190823.html\">L\u0110B\u0110 T\u00e2y Ban Nha n\u00e0i n\u1ec9 Pique \u0111\u1eebng chia tay \u0110TQG</span><br>\r\nGerard Pique chia tay \u0110T T\u00e2y Ban Nha sau World Cup 2018 l\u00e0 d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, song L\u0110B\u0110 x\u1ee9 s\u1edf B\u00f2 t\u00f3t mu\u1ed1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Barca thay \u0111\u1ed5i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4544","checkdouble":"191881"}]}